File name segmtalg.doc

this file describes the Storm Segments/Components Algorithm.

DESCRIPTION
        The storm segments/components algorithm identifies the radial sequences
        (segments) and ouputs the information on these segments. Segments are
        defined by seven reflectivity thresholds, ranging from 30 to 60 dbz.

